profile: Green Thumbs Landscaping and Lawn Service was founded by Douglas Blair.  The owner has over 10 years of lawn servicing experience. Douglas is an expert in maintenance services such as hedge trimming, mowing, edging, and weeding. He also takes on weed control, aeration, over seeding as well as hardscapes including mulching, garden beds, patios, walk ways, and more. He is comfortable working with all kinds of materials to achieve the dream landscape you're looking for.
name: Green Thumbs Landscaping and Lawn Service
